{subhead} Submit{def}
{p} {p}
{left}
{pp}

 AIO is a freely run magazine and for it to stay that way we always
like to see you the readers helping out by sending us your work for
inclusion into an issue of AIO. We except reviews, news, articles,
games/utilities reviews, title screens, music and anything else you
want to send to us.
{pp}
If you have anything you would like to submit to AIO you can do so
by sending it to the following places below. Your work will go on
the latest issue up to a day before release, so send your work any
time and its bound to get on the latest issue.
{pp}
 Below are details on how to submit your own work.
{pp}
Email : {bold}general@aioworld.com{nobold} (attach or just plain text)
{pp}
Web   : {bold}{link http://www.aioworld.com}http://www.aioworld.com{end}{nobold} (submit by mailto: )
